%N A395947 Expansion of e.g.f.: x*sinh(x)^2*cosh(x) (odd powers only).
%C A395947 Number of strings of length 2*n-1 defined on {0,1,2,3} with an odd number of 0's, an odd number of 1's, an even number of 2's and exactly one 3.
%H A395947 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (20,-118,180,-81).
%F A395947 a(n) = (2*n-1) * (3^(2*n-2)-1) / 4.
